she's all right.

357
00:31:21,712 --> 00:31:23,011
Ashley?

358
00:31:23,013 --> 00:31:24,345
Dad!

359
00:31:30,887 --> 00:31:31,785
Ashley, you're all right.

360
00:31:31,787 --> 00:31:35,021
