386
00:33:24,613 --> 00:33:28,181
That it was locked in the
deepest recesses of your mind.

387
00:33:52,072 --> 00:33:55,840
It's ok, dad.
I'll help you dig to China.

388
00:34:03,047 --> 00:34:03,445
Dad!

389
00:34:03,447 --> 00:34:08,149
